paragraphs.title: Create feature extractor
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.{CountVectorizer, IDF, Word2Vec}
import org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline
import com.github.uosdmlab.nkp.Tokenizer

val tokenizer = new Tokenizer()
    .setInputCol("document")
    .setOutputCol("words")

val cv = new CountVectorizer()
    .setInputCol("words")
    .setOutputCol("tf")

val idf = new IDF()
    .setInputCol("tf")
    .setOutputCol("tfidf")
    
val w2v = new Word2Vec()
    .setInputCol("words")
    .setOutputCol("vector")
    .setWindowSize(10)
    .setVectorSize(300)
    .setMaxIter(5)

val featureExtractor = new Pipeline()
  .setStages(Array(tokenizer, cv, idf, w2v))
  .fit(train)

featureExtractor.save("nsmc/model/feature_extractor")

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.PipelineModel

val featureExtractor = PipelineModel.load("nsmc/model/feature_extractor")

val trainFeature = featureExtractor.transform(train)

paragraphs.title: Train classifiers with TF
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.{NaiveBayes, LinearSVC}

val tfNB = new NaiveBayes()
    .setFeaturesCol("tf")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
tfNB.save("nsmc/model/tf-nb")
    
val tfSVC = new LinearSVC()
    .setFeaturesCol("tf")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
tfSVC.save("nsmc/model/tf-svc")

paragraphs.title: Train classifiers with TF-IDF
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.{NaiveBayes, LinearSVC}

    .setFeaturesCol("tfidf")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
tfidfNB.save("nsmc/model/tfidf-nb")

val tfidfSVC = new LinearSVC()
    .setFeaturesCol("tfidf")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
tfidfSVC.save("nsmc/model/tfidf-svc")

paragraphs.title: Train classifiers with word embedding
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.{LogisticRegression, LinearSVC, MultilayerPerceptronClassifier}

val vecLR = new LogisticRegression()
    .setFeaturesCol("vector")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
vecLR.save("nsmc/model/vec-lr")

val vecMLP = new MultilayerPerceptronClassifier()
    .setFeaturesCol("vector")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .setLayers(Array(300, 128, 64, 32, 2))
    .fit(trainFeature)
vecMLP.save("nsmc/model/vec-mlp")

val vecSVC = new LinearSVC()
    .setFeaturesCol("vector")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    .fit(trainFeature)
vecSVC.save("nsmc/model/vec-svc")

paragraphs.title: Evaluate
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.evaluation.MulticlassClassificationEvaluator
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.ClassificationModel

val evaluator = new MulticlassClassificationEvaluator()
    .setMetricName("accuracy")

val tfNBAcc = evaluator.evaluate(tfNB.transform(testFeature))
val tfSVCAcc = evaluator.evaluate(tfSVC.transform(testFeature))
val tfidfNBAcc = evaluator.evaluate(tfidfNB.transform(testFeature))
val tfidfSVCAcc = evaluator.evaluate(tfidfSVC.transform(testFeature))
val vecLRAcc = evaluator.evaluate(vecLR.transform(testFeature))
val vecMLPAcc = evaluator.evaluate(vecMLP.transform(testFeature))
val vecSVCAcc = evaluator.evaluate(vecSVC.transform(testFeature))
